Propane Delivery, Service & Equipment | Southern LP Gas Products












































































Go to Top














Southern LP Gas









Products & Services













When It Comes To Propane Delivery, Service, Equipment and Appliances, Call Southern LP Gas, the Propane Professionals!
Our friendly and competent staff is ready to help by answering your questions and finding solutions to meet all your propane gas related needs. Whether it’s installation, service/repair, delivery or finding that special propane appliance or equipment for your home or business, contact your local Southern LP Gas branch for immediate assistance.  We sell and service these and other products:








































 




Residence: Space Heaters Tankless Water Heaters Fireplace Systems Firebox Inserts Gas Log Sets Gas Stoves Installation Supplies






















 




Outdoor Living: Outdoor Fireplace Fire Pits Patio Heaters Gas Lights Holland Gas Grills Outdoor Cookers Installation Supplies






 Commercial: Infrared Heaters Tube Heaters Forced Air Heaters Burner Applications Forklift Fuel Parts Forklift Cylinder Parts Agriculture Heaters Swine Operation Heaters Installation Supplies






Services We Provide: Prompt Automatic Delivery Service Budget Payment Plans Propane Tank Rental Trained / Certified Technicians Certified Service Department Professional Equipment Installation/Repair Bottle Filling Services Gas Appliance Repair





















 









 
Tank Sales and Rentals
We deliver propane gas to both customer-owned tanks and company-owned rental tanks.
Renting a tank is always a great option. Have the peace of mind of renting a tank from Southern LP Gas. Did you know that propane gas regulations are constantly changing? Let the experts at Southern LP Gas keep your tank up-to-date. Also, when you rent a tank from us, we provide you with full maintenance, which includes painting and even costly parts – at no extra charge to you.
 
On-Demand Delivery and Auto-Delivery
Auto-Delivery
We refill your tank on a regular basis through our automated route system. This option includes On-Demand Delivery, so you never run out of gas. Stay warm, and never worry about checking your gas gauge again.
On-Demand Delivery
Call us or place an order on our website. Gas is delivered the next day to most locations. Our delivery personnel are always helpful and will provide a free quick- inspection of your equipment with every delivery.
 
Repair
Southern LP Gas differs from large corporate retailers in the sense that we offer Service After the Sale, including service of the manufacturers warranties. We care about the products that we sell. We always follow up with our customers to perform any needed adjustments and assure complete satisfaction. By buying equipment from Southern LP Gas, you get more for your money.
We also offer comprehensive repair on all lines and equipment that you already own. Our qualified technicians are very experienced in the repair and maintenance of propane systems and equipment. They constantly go through extensive on-the-job training, and attend State and National training and safety programs.
 
Propane Service in Arkansas and Louisiana
Offering propane service to customers nearby in the cities of DeQueen, Mena, Nashville, Bismarck, Hope, Lewisville, Fordyce, El Dorado, Monticello, Winnfield, Natchitoches, and Jonesville. Contact us to find out if Southern LP Gas offers Propane Equipment, Service, and Deliveries near you!
Payment Plans
We offer budget-billing, pay-as-you-go, financing with good credit, and we accept all major credit cards.















                    
                                        
                        © 2017 Southern LP Gas


